				<div class="bookname">
					<h1> 第1章 流落孤岛</h1>
					<div class="bottem1">
						<a href="javascript:;" onclick="showpop('/modules/article/uservote.php?id=5417&ajax_request=1');">投推荐票</a> <a href="/5_5417/">上一章</a> &larr; <a href="http://www.booktxt.net/5_5417/">章节目录</a> &rarr; <a href="/5_5417/2020674.html">下一章</a> <a href="javascript:;" onclick="showpop('/modules/article/addbookcase.php?id=5417&cid=2020673&ajax_request=1');">加入书签</a>
